<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038606" n="172v"/>
<p> <lb/>Diu est quod nihil litterarum ad Te dedi, Vir Amicissime, cujus rei causa
                    <lb/>fuit, quod semper expectabam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te responsionem ad ultimam meam
    <lb/><rs type="letter" key="B_1720-08-10_991170517025305501">epistolam</rs>, in qua pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter alia significavi, me Tibi transmisisse
    <lb/>petitas <rs key="pers_DE-588-12209025X" type="person">Werenfelsii</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_43V6EF8W">Dissertationes</rs>, quas Tibi jam dudum traditas esse
    <lb/>nullus dubito; amicus ille, qui pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dictas <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_43V6EF8W">dissertationes</rs> una cum alio
                    <lb/>fasciculo, quem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> acceperat, secum tulit <rs key="place_GEO-2659836" type="place">Luganum</rs> usque
                    <lb/>vel <rs key="place_GEO-3173435" type="place">Mediolanum</rs>, solvit 3<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> libras Venetas<note type="editorial">Libra veneta =</note> pro portorio usque ad 
                    <pb facs="1038607" n="173r"/>
    <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs>, quas una cum 8<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> libris, quibus constant ips<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_43V6EF8W">Dissertatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-12209025X" type="person">Werenfelsii</rs>, <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Agnato</rs> meo restituere poteris. Gau<subst><del><gap/></del><add>deo</add></subst><del> quod Libru</del>
    <lb/><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79"><subst><del>T</del><add>L</add></subst>ibrum</rs> Tuum jam dudum prodiisse, et gratias ago maximas pro exem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>plari, quod mihi per <rs key="place_GEO-3173435" type="place">Mediolani</rs> viam transmisisti, licet illud non<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dum acceperim; accepit quidem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> <rs type="letter" key="B_1721-05-30_991170515150105501">epistolam</rs>
                    aliquam Tuam,
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cum fasciculo <rs type="biblios" key="biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_JAFFCHKU biblio_M3G2JA79">libros</rs> tuos continente conjuncta erat, sed ipsum
                    <lb/>fasciculum non accepit, quod mirati sumus. Quod attinet ad objectio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccati</rs>, quam Tibi fecit pro vindicanda veritate corollarii 2<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>
    <abbr>prop.</abbr> 37<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Lib. 2<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_6CP8LL78"><abbr>Princ.</abbr>
<rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newt.</rs></rs> sententia mea adhuc est, quod vis
                    <lb/>generans aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> motum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis sit ponderi cylindri aquei, cujus
                    <lb/>altitudo sit <formula>=GJ</formula>, et basis = orificio <formula>EF</formula>. <subst><del>Aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></del><add>Gutt<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add></subst> enim exilientis
                    <lb/>motus generatur <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> pressione aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> incumbentis, et h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c pressio
                    <lb/>est <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis ponderi cylindri aquei pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dictam altitudinem <formula>GJ</formula>
<lb/>habentis et<del> ba</del> cujus basis est <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis latitudini gutt<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> elabentis.
                    <lb/>Fingamus <add>in</add> fund<subst><del>um</del><add>o va</add></subst>sis horizontali<del>s</del> particulam aliquam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem
                    <lb/>orificio <formula>EF</formula>, constat pressionem aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in hanc particulam esse
                    <lb/><formula>=</formula> ponderi cylindri <formula>EF \times GJ</formula>, jam vero gutt<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> omnes per orifici<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>um <formula>EF</formula><del> elabe</del> simul elabentes eodem modo ab aqua incumbente
                    <lb/>premuntur ac particula fundi cujus magnitudo est <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis
                    <lb/>orificio <formula>EF</formula>, ergo guttarum omnium per orificium <formula>EF</formula> simul
                    <lb/>elabentium motus totus generatur <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> pressione ponderis <formula>EF \times GJ</formula>.
                    <lb/>Concedo autem aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> egress<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quantitatem tempore, quo grave
                    <lb/>motu accelerato describit lineam <formula>GJ</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem esse column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                    <formula>EF \times 2GJ</formula>, sed non video quomodo hinc sequatur, vim aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>motum generantem esse <formula>= EF \times 2GJ</formula>, ut statuit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119543885" type="person">Riccatus</rs> cum
                    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Newtono</rs>. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs> dixit se de hac re mentem suam exposuisse
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">filio</rs><note type="internal">ToDo: Kontrollieren, da Daniel I B. auch in die Riccati-Kontroverse verwickelt war.</note>, qui eam Tibi sine dubio jam aperuit, amplius tamen de
                    <pb facs="1038608" n="173v"/>
<lb/>eadem re ad Te scripturum promisit, quamprimum Dissertatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem Tuam acceperit. Salutem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so dic plurimam amicis et
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">adgnato</rs><note type="internal">ToDo: Wer war zu diesem Zeitpunkt in Venedig? Nic. II B. oder Dan. I B.?</note> meo, cui brevi scribam gratulaturus ipsi de <rs key="pers_DE-588-1090746725" type="person">fratre</rs> re<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cens nato. </p><closer><salute>Vale et me amare perge.</salute> <dateline><abbr>Dab.</abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1721-07-02">2. <abbr>Jul.</abbr> 1721</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
</body>
